  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies the CICP (Coding-Independent Code Points) color primaries for a color space.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

CICP (Coding-Independent Code Points) primaries are defined in ITU-T H.273 / ISO 23091-2 and identify the color gamut of a color space. Used with <xref:M:SkiaSharp.SKColorSpace.CreateCicp*>.
]]></format></remarks>
